snippet.title: Nemesis: Lockdown - Official Overview Trailer
snippet.description: Learn more about Nemesis: Lockdown, including how to utilize locations to your advantage, the importance of your cards, and more in this game overview trailer. Nemesis: Lockdown, the CRPG based on the board game, is available on PC via Steam today, November 17, 2022.
